    Title: I Ching
  Title: The Man of Many Qualities
Title: Organizational Growth Pains
---
The man wanders aimlessly without adequate guidance, like a hunter without
a forester. The superior man knows when going forward will cause regret. He
gives up the senseless chase and avoids eventual disgrace.
